headline: A Close Matchup and a Potential Upset
abstract: In the first round, all but one home team is favored. Could red-hot Tennessee pull off an upset at New England?
lead_paragraph: Seventeen weeks of preamble led to this. Eight N.F.L. teams will fight for a chance to move on from a wild-card round that features the winners of the last three Super Bowls and that has one game in which the road team is favored.
